                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>PS: postage I'll pay of all Letters on ac of this correspondence;\n                                        that I may<lb/> not be too <sic>burthensome</sic> to an\n                                        utter stranger of the subscriber<lb/> In the above I forgot\n                                        to ask whether <persName>Jesus</persName>—came for the\n                                        purpose of<lb/> redeeming the Jews with other's of\n                                        mankind.–</p>"
